<TEXT>Year 882 (DCCCLXXXII) was a common year starting on Monday (link will display the full calendar) of the Julian calendar.
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>52446_3</DOCNO>
<TEXT><onlyinclude>
</TEXT>
